  "data": {
    "number": 73,
    "name": "سُورَةُ المُزَّمِّلِ",
    "englishName": "Al-Muzzammil",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Enshrouded One",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 20,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 5476,
        "text": "披衣的人啊！",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 574,
        "ruku": 508,
        "hizbQuarter": 229,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5477,
        "text": "你应当在夜间礼拜，除开不多的时间，",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 574,
        "ruku": 508,
        "hizbQuarter": 229,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5478,
        "text": "半夜或少一点，",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 574,
        "ruku": 508,
        "hizbQuarter": 229,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5479,
        "text": "或多一点。你应当讽诵《古兰经》，",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 574,
        "ruku": 508,
        "hizbQuarter": 229,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5480,
        "text": "我必定以庄严的言辞授予你，",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 574,
        "ruku": 508,
        "hizbQuarter": 229,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5481,
        "text": "夜间的觉醒确是更适当的；夜间的讽诵确是更正确的。",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 574,
        "ruku": 508,
        "hizbQuarter": 229,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5482,
        "text": "你在白天忙於事务，",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 574,
        "ruku": 508,
        "hizbQuarter": 229,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5483,
        "text": "故你应当纪念你的主的尊名，你应当专心致志地敬事他。",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 574,
        "ruku": 508,
        "hizbQuarter": 229,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5484,
        "text": "他是东方和西方的主，除他之外，绝无应受崇拜的，故你应当以他为监护者。",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 574,
        "ruku": 508,
        "hizbQuarter": 229,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5485,
        "text": "你应当忍受他们所说的谰言，而温和地退避他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 574,
        "ruku": 508,
        "hizbQuarter": 229,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5486,
        "text": "你让我处治享受安乐而否认真理的人们吧！你稍稍地宽待他们吧！",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 574,
        "ruku": 508,
        "hizbQuarter": 229,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5487,
        "text": "我那里确有沉重的镣和强烈的火，",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 574,
        "ruku": 508,
        "hizbQuarter": 229,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5488,
        "text": "有噎人的食物，和痛苦的刑罚。",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 574,
        "ruku": 508,
        "hizbQuarter": 229,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5489,
        "text": "在那日，天地和山峦都要震动，而山峦将要变成一堆散沙。",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 574,
        "ruku": 508,
        "hizbQuarter": 229,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5490,
        "text": "我确已派遣一个使者来教化你们，而且对你们作证，犹如我曾派遣一个使者去教化法老一样。",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 574,
        "ruku": 508,
        "hizbQuarter": 229,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5491,
        "text": "但法老违抗了那个使者，故我严厉地惩治了他。",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 574,
        "ruku": 508,
        "hizbQuarter": 229,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5492,
        "text": "如果你们不信道，那末，你们怎么防备那将使儿童白发苍苍的日子呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 574,
        "ruku": 508,
        "hizbQuarter": 229,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5493,
        "text": "天将为那日而破裂，真主的应许要实现的。",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 574,
        "ruku": 508,
        "hizbQuarter": 229,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5494,
        "text": "这确是一种教训。谁愿意觉悟，谁可以选择一条通达主的道路。",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 574,
        "ruku": 508,
        "hizbQuarter": 229,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 5495,
        "text": "你的主的确知道你礼拜的时间，不到全夜的三分之二，或二分之一，或三分之一。你的同道中，有一群人也是那样做的。真主预定黑夜和白昼的长度，他知道你们不能计算它，故赦宥你们。你们应当诵《古兰经》中简易的（文辞）。他知道你们中将有一些病人，和别的许多人，或旅行四方，寻求真主的恩惠；或为真主而作战，故你们应当讽诵其中简易的（文辞）。你们应当谨守拜功，完纳天课，并以善债借给真主。你们为自己做什么善事，都将在真主那里得到更好更大的报酬。你们应当向真主求饶，真主是至赦的，是至慈的。",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 29,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 575,
        "ruku": 509,
        "hizbQuarter": 230,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
